				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>2011年炸药物理奖：</p>
<p>The 2011 Nobel Prize in Physics is awarded &#8220;for the discovery of the accelerating expansion of the Universe through observations of distant supernovae&#8221; with one half to Saul Perlmutter and the other half jointly to Brian P. Schmidt and Adam G. Riess.</p>
<p>下面是三个人的照片：</p>
<p><div id="attachment_2246" style="width: 172px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/perlmutter.jpg"><img src="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/perlmutter.jpg" alt="" title="Perlmutter" width="162" height="227" class="size-full wp-image-2246" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Perlmutter</p></div><br />
<strong>Saul Perlmutter</strong></p>
<p><strong>Born</strong>: 1959, Champaign-Urbana, IL, USA</p>
<p><strong>Affiliation at the time of the award</strong>: Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory, Berkeley, CA, USA, University of California, Berkeley, CA, USA</p>
<div id="attachment_2247" style="width: 172px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/schmidt.jpg"><img src="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/schmidt.jpg" alt="" title="Schmidt" width="162" height="227" class="size-full wp-image-2247" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Schmidt</p></div>
<p><strong>Brian P. Schmidt<br />
</strong><br />
<strong>Born</strong>: 1967, Missoula, MT, USA</p>
<p><strong>Affiliation at the time of the award</strong>: Australian National University, Weston Creek, Australia</p>
<div id="attachment_2248" style="width: 172px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/riess.jpg"><img src="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/riess.jpg" alt="" title="Riess" width="162" height="227" class="size-full wp-image-2248" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Riess</p></div>
<p><strong>Adam G. Riess</strong></p>
<p><strong>Born</strong>: 1969, Washington, DC, USA</p>
<p><strong>Affiliation at the time of the award</strong>: Johns Hopkins University, Baltimore, MD, USA, Space Telescope Science Institute, Baltimore, MD, USA</p>
<p>来张Saul Perlmutter的震撼照片：<br />
<a href="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/perlmutter_supernova_ladder_slideshow.jpg"><img src="http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/perlmutter_supernova_ladder_slideshow.jpg" alt="" title="perlmutter_supernova_ladder_slideshow" width="515" height="300" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2249" /></a></p>
